###############################################################################
### BEGIN SECTION EXTENSION SWITCHES
###############################################################################
###
### This section lists all emission extensions available to HEMCO and whether 
### they shall be used or not. Extension 'base' must have extension number 
### zero, all other extension numbers can be freely chosen. Data fields in 
### section 'base emissions' will only be read if the corresponding extension 
### (identified by ExtNr) is enabled. Similarly, fields grouped into data 
### collections ('(((CollectionName', ')))CollectionName') are only considered
### if the corresponding data collection is enabled in this section.
###
### All species to be used by HEMCO can be given explicitly in the Species 
### section of extension 'Base'. For example,
###
### 0       Base              : on    NO/NO2/CO
###
### will only activate NO, NO2 and CO as HEMCO species. All other fields will 
### be ignored entirely. This is even true for species only used in another 
### extension. For instance, if the dust emission extension shall be used, 
### the dust species must be set explicitly as base species:
###
### 0       Base              : on    NO/NO2/CO/DST1/DST2/DST3/DST4
###
### The wildcard character can be used to use all possible species (species 
### used in  HEMCO and defined by GEOS-Chem). This is recommended:
###
### 0       Base              : on    *
###
### Make sure that the ExtNr provided here matches with the ExtNr provided in 
### the base emissions sections. Otherwise, the listed files won't be read!
###
###############################################################################
# ExtNr ExtName           on/off  Species
0       Base              : on    *
    --> GENERIC           :       false
    --> ANNUAL            :       false
    --> MONTHLY           :       true
    --> BBIO_DIURNAL      :       false
    --> BBIO_DAILY        :       true
    --> BIOFUEL           :       true
    --> NET_TERR_EXCH     :       true
    --> SHIP              :       true
    --> CO2CORR           :       true
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ExtNr ExtName           on/off  Species 
111     GFED3             : on    CO2bb
    --> CO scale factor   :       1.05
112     GFED3_daily       : on    -
113     GFED3_3hourly     : off   -
114     FINN              : off   CO2bb
115     FINN_daily        : on 

END SECTION EXTENSION SWITCHES


